file: crates/ctx-cage/tests/bwrap_build.rs
purpose: Argv-shape tests for `build_bwrap_args`. Verifies flag presence, bind mounts, env vars, and command placement without invoking `bwrap`.
invariants:
  - All tests are pure; no subprocess is spawned.
external_deps:
  - ctx_cage::bwrap: module under test, plus its path constants
  - common: test helpers (`has_pair`, `has_ro_bind`, `has_setenv`, `has_tmpfs`, `sample_claude_binds`, `sample_config`)
functions: